{"title":"git版本控制与hexo创建站点学习记录","date":"2019-03-19T08:46:30.000Z","slug":"page","comments":true,"tags":["git","github","hexo","terminal"],"categories":["Hexo"],"updated":"2019-04-24T09:38:48.334Z","content":"<p><a class=\"headFigure\" href=\"/post/page\"><img src=\"http://img.zqt0510.cn/19-03-26-de302a66e34f78b28102e019d2da6d17.png\" alt=\"截图\"></a></p>\n<h1 id=\"git版本控制与hexo创建站点学习记录\"><a href=\"/post/page\">git版本控制与hexo创建站点学习记录</a><a href=\"post/page#git版本控制与hexo创建站点学习记录\"></a></h1><p>安装Hexo相当简单。然而在安装前，您必须检查电脑中是否已安装下列应用程序</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Node.js</li>\n<li>Git</li>\n<li>npm</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">MosesdeMBP:git_Github moseslbell$ git --version</span><br><span class=\"line\">git version 2.17.0</span><br><span class=\"line\">MosesdeMBP:git_Github moseslbell$ mkdir test</span><br><span class=\"line\">MosesdeMBP:git_Github moseslbell$ rm -rdf test</span><br><span class=\"line\">MosesdeMBP:git_Github moseslbell$</span><br><span class=\"line\">MosesdeMBP:git_Github moseslbell$ git init</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"git三种添加版本方式\">git三种添加版本方式<a href=\"post/page#git三种添加版本方式\"></a></h2><p>添加新修改的<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">MosesdeMBP:git_Github moseslbell$ git add .</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<p>添加修改过的/删除过的<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">MosesdeMBP:git_Github moseslbell$ git add -u</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>添加全部所有的内容<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">MosesdeMBP:git_Github moseslbell$ git add -A</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<hr>\n<h4 id=\"添加新的版本及说明\">添加新的版本及说明<a href=\"post/page#添加新的版本及说明\"></a></h4><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git commit -m ‘添加提交版本说明信息’</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"提交到-github-及查看状态\">提交到 github 及查看状态<a href=\"post/page#提交到-github-及查看状态\"></a></h2><p>提交到 github 服务器上面 master主分支<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git push -u origin master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>查看提交的状态<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git status</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>查看之前提交的所有版本日志信息<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git reflog</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<h2 id=\"修改及撤销git版本的操作\">修改及撤销git版本的操作<a href=\"post/page#修改及撤销git版本的操作\"></a></h2><p>返回之前添加过的版本</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git reset --hard */b6b4ba5/*  后面的是版本号</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>直接返回上一个添加的版本<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git reset --hard HEAD^</span><br><span class=\"line\">git reset --hard HEAD^^  返回上两个版本</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>添加暂存后  /  撤销修改<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git add . </span><br><span class=\"line\">git checkout -- a.txt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>移除暂存区的缓存文件信息<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git rm --cache a.txt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"提交到远程的github仓库\">提交到远程的github仓库<a href=\"post/page#提交到远程的github仓库\"></a></h2><p>提交到远程的github上面的指定仓库地址<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git remote add origin https://github.com/Jerry318/file_version.git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>通常先下载服务器上代码到本地<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git pull</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>再提交本地代码push上传到服务器<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git push -u origin master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"切换git分支\">切换git分支<a href=\"post/page#切换git分支\"></a></h2><p>切换git分支—后面 “test” 是分支名称<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git checkout -b test</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>查看现有的版本分支<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git branch</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>切换回到主分支上<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git checkout master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>本地创建新的分支<br>git checkout -b branchname(直接新建一个分支然后切换至新创建的分支).就是创建加切换分支.<br>等价于命令：git branch branchname+git checkout branchname.</p>\n<p>将新分支推送至GitHub服务器<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git push origin branch-name</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>合并次分支代码到主分支上  “test001”  分支名称<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git merge test001</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>删除不需要的分支代码文件  “test001”  分支名称<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git  branch -D test001</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"如果不需要这个仓库时可以在设置中进行删除\">如果不需要这个仓库时可以在设置中进行删除<a href=\"post/page#如果不需要这个仓库时可以在设置中进行删除\"></a></h2><div class=\"article-img\"><p><img src=\"http://img.zqt0510.cn/19-03-26-2b569e42389c73086950759dcb65a01a.png\" alt=\"截图\" data-zoomable></p></div>\n<h3 id=\"找到底部的信息\">找到底部的信息<a href=\"post/page#找到底部的信息\"></a></h3><div class=\"article-img\"><p><img src=\"http://img.zqt0510.cn/19-03-26-e8e855490a6b9fe966f58b2feb0d7fdd.png\" alt=\"截图\" data-zoomable></p></div>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"安装与启用Hexo流程\">安装与启用Hexo流程<a href=\"post/page#安装与启用Hexo流程\"></a></h2><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install hexo-cli -g</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo init blog</span><br><span class=\"line\">cd blog</span><br><span class=\"line\">npm install</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo clean 删除缓存</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo generate  生成静态页面</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo server  在本地启用服务</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo new page  创建新的页面</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"简书上找的资料\">简书上找的资料<a href=\"post/page#简书上找的资料\"></a></h2><ol>\n<li><p>创建一般的文章：hexo new “文章名称”</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>创建”关于我”等页面：hexo new page “about”这里的about要和在主题的_config.yml文件中的menu中进行匹配</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<blockquote>\n<pre><code>如: menu:\n    Home: /\n    Archives: /archives\n    About: /about\n</code></pre></blockquote>\n<p> 那创建关于我的页面：hexo new page “about” 在编辑创建出来的md文件，然后部署就能看到</p>\n<ol>\n<li>创建友情链接：在主题的配置中：</li>\n</ol>\n<blockquote>\n<pre><code>links_title: 友情链接\nlinks:\n</code></pre></blockquote>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"发布到github远程服务器仓库\">发\b布到github远程服务器仓库<a href=\"post/page#发布到github远程服务器仓库\"></a></h2><p>根目录安装hexo-deployer-git插件</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install hexo-deployer-git —save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>上传到远程github指定分支的服务器仓库</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo  deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>官方文档链接说明<br>/# Deployment/<br>/## Docs: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/deployment.html/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://hexo.io/docs/deployment.html/</a></p>\n<p>根目录_config.yml添加关联信息</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">deploy:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  type: git</span><br><span class=\"line\">  repo: git@github.com:Jerry318/design.github.io.git</span><br><span class=\"line\">  branch: master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"git–SSH–keys密钥的创建顺序\">git–SSH–keys密钥的创建顺序<a href=\"post/page#git–SSH–keys密钥的创建顺序\"></a></h2><div class=\"article-img\"><p><img src=\"http://img.zqt0510.cn/19-03-26-fcfa59dcb3b6cfb464ae54c514a72a14.png\" alt=\"截图\" data-zoomable></p></div>\n<p>首先在本地创建 SSHKeys<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ ssh-keygen -t rsa -C “18817801185@163.com”</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>后面的邮箱即为 github 注册邮箱，之后会要求确认路径和输入密码，一路回车就行。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">cd ~/.ssh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>出现提示 “No such file or directory”，此时可以选择手动创建一个 .ssh 文件夹</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">MosesdeMBP:~ moseslbell$ cd ~/.ssh</span><br><span class=\"line\">MosesdeMBP:.ssh moseslbell$ ls</span><br><span class=\"line\">id_rsa\t##密钥## id_rsa.pub ##公钥## known_hosts known_hosts2</span><br><span class=\"line\">MosesdeMBP:.ssh moseslbell$ vim id_rsa.pub</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"git版本控制管理\">git版本控制管理<a href=\"post/page#git版本控制管理\"></a></h2><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git tag 设置版本标签     </span><br><span class=\"line\">git tag v1.0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>查看所有标签信息<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git tag</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>查看添加过版本记录信息<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git show v1.0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>删除版本标签信息<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git tag -d v1.0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"git版本控制桌面GUI工具说明\">git版本控制桌面GUI工具说明:<a href=\"post/page#git版本控制桌面GUI工具说明\"></a></h2><p>工具下载链接 <a href=\"https://desktop.github.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://desktop.github.com/</a></p>\n<div class=\"article-img\"><p><img src=\"http://img.zqt0510.cn/19-03-26-58920fcbff016b0a95066b87ade9a0fc.png\" alt=\"截图\" data-zoomable></p></div>\n<p>工具界面</p>\n<div class=\"article-img\"><p><img src=\"http://img.zqt0510.cn/19-03-26-837692c3dc1d70b94826d1d055cff987.png\" alt=\"截图\" data-zoomable></p></div>\n<p>菜单创建界面<br><img src=\"http://img.zqt0510.cn/19-03-26-a954f31778b4db2bf0cb3c1a24a92e2a.png\" alt=\"截图\"></p>\n<pre><code>1. 创建一个线上仓库   2. 添加一个本地的仓库   3. 克隆一个线上仓库\n</code></pre><p>添加git版本信息操作按钮及push到远程仓库按钮位置<br><img src=\"http://img.zqt0510.cn/19-03-26-1365d3c7ef10a4033fe7c1ab552a9f60.png\" alt=\"截图\"></p>\n<p>添加git版本分支按钮位置<br><img src=\"http://img.zqt0510.cn/19-03-26-c6dc92956db9f892db5b1804de8cf824.png\" alt=\"截图\"></p>\n","prev":{"title":"有哪些好看的 Hexo 主题？","slug":"Hexo-Themes"},"next":{"title":"Hello World","slug":"hello-world"},"link":"http://www.zqt0510.cn/post/page/","toc":[{"title":"<a>git版本控制与hexo创建站点学习记录</a>","id":"git版本控制与hexo创建站点学习记录","index":"1","children":[{"title":"git三种添加版本方式","id":"git三种添加版本方式","index":"1.1"},{"title":"提交到 github 及查看状态","id":"提交到-github-及查看状态","index":"1.2"},{"title":"修改及撤销git版本的操作","id":"修改及撤销git版本的操作","index":"1.3"},{"title":"提交到远程的github仓库","id":"提交到远程的github仓库","index":"1.4"},{"title":"切换git分支","id":"切换git分支","index":"1.5"},{"title":"如果不需要这个仓库时可以在设置中进行删除","id":"如果不需要这个仓库时可以在设置中进行删除","index":"1.6","children":[{"title":"找到底部的信息","id":"找到底部的信息","index":"1.6.1"}]},{"title":"安装与启用Hexo流程","id":"安装与启用Hexo流程","index":"1.7"},{"title":"简书上找的资料","id":"简书上找的资料","index":"1.8"},{"title":"发\b布到github远程服务器仓库","id":"发布到github远程服务器仓库","index":"1.9"},{"title":"git–SSH–keys密钥的创建顺序","id":"git–SSH–keys密钥的创建顺序","index":"1.10"},{"title":"git版本控制管理","id":"git版本控制管理","index":"1.11"},{"title":"git版本控制桌面GUI工具说明:","id":"git版本控制桌面GUI工具说明","index":"1.12"}]}],"copyright":{"author":"Jerry","link":"<a href=\"http://www.zqt0510.cn/post/page/\" title=\"git版本控制与hexo创建站点学习记录\">http://www.zqt0510.cn/post/page/</a>","license":"自由转载-非商用-禁止演绎-保持署名 (<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)"}}